      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SOUTH CRENSHAW (6) had the drop on the lead and went on to be beaten one length into second (16.20) at this track in a Grade 5 over 275m. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Ready to find winning form. LIBERTY STAR (2) has some solid form under her belt and proved too classy last time to win by half a length at this track in a handy 16.38 beating Like A Ferrari. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Has hit winning form and can go on with it. WILD MOOD (3) slotted in just off the lead from the wide draw last start and boxed on to finish third (17.56) at Northam in a Grade 5 over 297m. Comes through a solid form race last start. Hard to beat again. IMPRESS KERR (1) can play a role coming off a short let-up.",
